         <abstract>
            <p>We give the results of a computer search for maximally equidistributed combined linear feedback shift register (or Tausworthe) random number generators, whose components are trinomials of degrees slightly less than 32 or 64. These generators are fast and have good statistical properties.</p>
          </abstract>
